132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST SPECIAL SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 1686
H.P. 1121 House of Representatives, April 17, 2025
An Act to Clarify, Align and Amend Provisions of the Maine
Revised Statutes, Title 35-A
Submitted by the Public Utilities Commission pursuant to Joint Rule 204.
Reference to the Committee on Energy, Utilities and Technology suggested and ordered
printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
